item.title: The kickoff
item.description:
The Community Group has kicked off!

Thanks to everyone who joined us this afternoon - we hope you found it inspiring! Keen to join our Community? Please fill out the survey so we can get in touch!

In the meantime, have a look at the PAGE presentation and the draft ontology specification for more info on Thoughtflow. More to come soon!
